-- Philippine Equity Movers: Alliance Select, Dizon Copper, Roxas
-- B y   C e c i l i a   Y a p
-- 2012-09-18T04:44:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-18/philippine-equity-movers-alliance-select-dizon-copper-roxas.html
Philippine Stock Exchange Index
falls 0.3% at noon break, halts four-day advance; 20 stocks
decline, 10 advance.  *Alliance Select (FOOD PM) +7.2%; Co. will seek to list as many
as 430.3m shares on Singapore Exchange Securities’s Catalist
Board, it says in stock-exchange disclosure  *Dizon Copper (DIZ PM) +3.7%; Capital Gold, Welcome Stranger
Mining to acquire exclusive mining, processing and operation
rights to Dizon’s copper, silver and gold tailings in Zambales
province, Dizon says in stock-exchange disclosure. Memorandum of
agreement signed yesterday, Dizon says.  *Roxas Holdings (ROX PM) +1.1% after declaring 6 centavos cash
dividend  To contact the reporter on this story:
